        <updateDate>2022-01-13T16:35:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Fix Funding First Act</strong></p> <p>This bill makes several modifications to the federal budget process. Among other modifications, the bill changes the dates of the fiscal year to match the calendar year; requires a biennial budget resolution that is signed into law by the President; and limits congressional pay, recesses, and travel if the budget resolution and the appropriations bills have not been enacted within specified time frames. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
